snippet.title: Twitter Account Location Flag Chrome Extension  #github
snippet.description:
Here’s a Chrome extension you didn’t know you needed until right now. It adds country flags next to every Twitter — sorry, X — username… automatically. As you scroll, it quietly pulls each account’s public location through Twitter’s GraphQL API, figures out the country, and drops a clean little flag emoji right next to the handle. 

https://github.com/RhysSullivan/twitter-account-location-in-username

#github #opensource
